{"tid":2252123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉暴動罪流亡 22歲中大女生獲政治庇護 稱遭難民營職員性侵","createTime":"2020-10-21T09:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T11:26:49.000Z","uid":306111,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2622c518784923468c0bf2b317cb6c386f9794a","tid":2252123,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:22:11.000Z","msg":"因旺角騷亂案潛逃德國、其後獲德國政府批出政治庇護的黃台仰和李東昇，早前發起組織「避風驛」（Haven Assistance），該組織今天（19日）在社交專頁公布，一名因參與反修例運動、被警方以暴動罪拘捕的22歲中大女學生，於本月14日收到德國聯邦移民與難民局通知，正式獲批政治庇護，該女生取得為期3年的難民身份。<br />\n<br />\n該名女生在德國入住難民營11個月，她向「避風驛」透露，在難民營居住期間，曾因情緒問題進出醫院，亦曾遭難民營職員性侵，但未有透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n醬汁<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201019/s00001/1603118679808/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86-%E7%A8%B1%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%AD%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%87%9F%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00001%2F1603118679808%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2587%259F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=5580bbc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201019%2Fs00001%2F1603118679808%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%2586-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2587%259F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5&h=1bdcfb8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.m